  "title": "Event Assistant!!!",
  "description": "<p>🌟Event Assistant!!!🌟<br /></p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for a responsible and enthusiastic Event Assistant to support our team during events. In this role, you will help with event setup, on-site operations, and pack-down to ensure everything runs smoothly. This is a great position for someone who enjoys teamwork and working in a fast-paced environment.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Support event staff with registration, guest assistance, and general coordination</li><li>Help keep the event area clean, organized, and safe</li><li>Provide support during event activities as directed by supervisors</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Good communication and teamwork skills</li><li>Positive attitude and willingness to learn</li><li>Able to work in a busy, fast-paced environment</li><li>Reliable, punctual, and flexible with working hours</li></ul>",
